www-subtext: Thola ukufinyelela ezimpendulweni ezivulekile eziyizigidi ezingu-1.2 ngale deshibhodi esebenzisanayo, ithuluzi eliyingqayizivele elixhumanisa amazwi abesifazane namantombazane kanye namathuba angapheli okuhlaziywa kwedijithali.
midwives-voices-subtext: Sabuza ababelethisi emhlabeni wonke lo mbuzo: “Yini oyifunayo kakhulu endimeni yakho yokuba umbelethisi?”
pmnch-subtext: Siyakwamukela Kudeshibhodi ethi "Lokho Okufunwa Yintsha"! Leli thuluzi elisebenzisanayo linikeza ukumelwa okubonakalayo kwezimpendulo kanye nemininingwane esiyiqoqayo kubantu abasha abaneminyaka engu-10-24 emhlabeni jikelele. Umnyombo wesinyathelo ngumbuzo ovulekile: "Ukuze ngithuthukise inhlalakahle yami, ngifuna ...". Abantu abasha abavela kuwo wonke umhlaba bebephendula lokhu, besinika ukuqonda okuyingqayizivele ngezidingo zabo, amathemba, kanye nezifiso zabo. Hlola idatha, thola izindaba ezingemuva kwezinombolo, futhi uhlanganyele nathi ekwandiseni amazwi abantu abasha abayizigidi eziyizinkulungwane eziyi-1.8 emhlabeni jikelele. Ukuze ufunde kabanzi mayelana nomkhankaso, vakashela ku-http://www.1point8.org.
